name: A Game of No Particular Subject
name_original: A Game of No Particular Subject
description:
Welcome to a game. Does it have any subjects? No. Is it scary? I don't know. Is it a platformer? I DON'T KNOW!

It's...a game of no particular subject.

I made this at 10 to 11 PM and as I am writing this description I'm really bored.
